    <h>bocsa</h>
    <p><g>bocsa</g>
        <en>box</en> is a masculine <a href="?xx=nouns/simple_common_nouns">simple common
        noun</a>.</p>

    <section>
        <h>forms</h>
        <p>The principal parts of <g>bocsa</g> are – <ul>
                <li><m>bocsa</m> – singular</li>
                <li><m>bocsaichean</m> – plural</li>
            </ul>
        </p>
