    <section>
        <h>uses</h>
        <section id="uses-sbj">
            <h>subject</h>
            <p>Like other nouns, <g>bocsa</g> can be used as the subject of a <a
                    href="?xx=verbs/verbs">verb</a>.</p>
            <p>Examples with <a href="?gd=bi"><g>bi</g></a> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Càit a bheil am <m>bocsa</m>? Tha am <m>bocsa</m> air a’ bhòrd.</gd>
                        <tr>Where is the box? The box is on the table.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 20</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
            <!--<p>Examples with demonstrative pronouns used as copular verbs – <xl>
